; Coverage test for post.cc
; Tests fn_any with second argument false to skip the current posting.
; any(expr, false) evaluates expr against all OTHER postings in the
; transaction, not including the current one. Here, the Expenses:Food
; posting itself is skipped so it doesn't match; only Assets:Cash
; (the other posting) sees that Expenses:Food matches.

2024/03/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food     $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/03/02 Transfer
    Assets:Savings    $100.00
    Assets:Checking

test reg --limit "any(account =~ /Expense/, false)"
24-Mar-01 Groceries             Assets:Cash                 $-10.00      $-10.00
end test
